reviewText: not up to rodney yees usual standards. there is another instructer included on a second work out  that I haven't tried yet

This is such a fun DVD -- Rodney is teasing and joking and laughing -- most relaxed DVD I've ever seen from him.  I teach a variety of Yoga and like to get new ideas from DVDs -- this was just what I needed. AND it is so fun I'll probably practice with it myself when I don't want to have to figure out my own routine. More like this would be great!
